<eesti> Eridirektiivide v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamisel kohaldatavad tervisekriteeriumid </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where appropriate, Positive lists of substances shall be established for materials and articles intended to come into contact with foodstuffs. </inglise>
<eesti> Vajaduse korral koostatakse toiduainetega kokkupuutumiseks etten&auml;htud materjalides ja toodetes lubatud ainete loetelud. </eesti>
<inglise> The acceptability of a substance for inclusion in a positive list shall be determined by considering both the quantity of the substance which is liable to migrate into foodstuffs and the toxicity of the substance </inglise>
